videos.description: LeBron James compliments the Pelicans on how hard they played, while also giving high praise to the young NBA stars. He also shares what winning the MVP this season would mean to him.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (LeBron strives to be an MVP every night) 2020/3/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron strives to be an MVP every night

videos.description: Alvin Gentry is astonished that other players could be considered for MVP, citing how much better LeBron James makes his team.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Gentry amazed players other than LeBron are being considered for MVP) 2020/3/1

videos.headline: Gentry amazed players other than LeBron are being considered for MVP

videos.description: LeBron James feels it's his responsibility to mentor young players in the league and says that if anyone has a problem with that, "tell them to kiss my ass... with a smile too."

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (LeBron says 'kiss my ass' to critics who think he's 'buddy-buddy' with opponents) 2020/3/1

videos.headline: LeBron says 'kiss my ass' to critics who think he's 'buddy-buddy' with opponents

videos.description: Zion Williamson shares how it feels to receive high praise from someone with a resume like LeBron James.
